edu.byu.ece.rapidSmith.bitstreamTools.examples
Class BitstreamManipulation

java.lang.Object
  edu.byu.ece.rapidSmith.bitstreamTools.examples.BitstreamManipulation

public class BitstreamManipulation
extends java.lang.Object

Implements the same bitstream manipulation routines that Ben Sellers created in his original bitmanip tool. This class demonstrates how to perform the same functions using the new API.
